To simplify \((\tfrac{y^4}{z^{10}})^5\), raise both numerator and denominator to the 5th power:

\[
(\tfrac{y^4}{z^{10}})^5 \;=\;\frac{(y^4)^5}{(z^{10})^5}
=\frac{y^{4\cdot5}}{z^{10\cdot5}}
=\frac{y^{20}}{z^{50}}.
\]

